{
  "stem": "20616.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Kanto, ?] our teacher, he came up to me and he said, I suggest you go right home.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Don't dawdle on the way and don't get involved in any conversations.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was very much surprised because I usually went right home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I may have-- may have walked together with somebody else and we may have stopped to meet somebody, but usually when I-- but he never said that before.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I didn't know why he would say that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I started to walk home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And shortly before we got to the house, there was a Jewish butcher store.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I noticed there was a crowd in front of the Jewish butcher store.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And also next to the butcher store was a box that displayed the [GERMAN], which was [GERMAN] anti-Semitic paper.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I don't-- can't call it a newspaper.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was a hate-- hate sheet more than anything else, with a very bad cartoons of caricatures of Jews and a Jew baiting paper.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And people were gathered around that, as well.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "In the past, I looked at that box occasionally and my mother had already told me, she said, if any people around that box, try to stay away from them.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That paper is not- that box has some very-- not very nice things written on it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I was curious once and I did stop by and looked at it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I thought the whole thing was rather silly, I didn't pay much attention to it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But when I got to the butcher store on the way home, I noticed that there was a Star of David was scrawled on there and Juden and placards were carried about saying, don't buy from Jews and so on.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I sort of walked around that group.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
